Package: waspas
Type: Package
Title: Toolset to implement WASPAS Based Multi-criteria decision analysis (MCDA) solutions
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Barbara", "Flavio", email = "flavio.barbara@gmail.com", role = c("cre","aut")),
    person("Santoa", "Marcos", email = marcosdossantos_doutorado_uff@yahoo.com.br", role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: flavio.barbara@gmail.com
Description: Provides a set of functions to implement decision-making systems based on the WASPAS method.
    Set data of Alternatives, valued according to Weighted Criteria common to the alternatives.
    These values must be continuous numeric. Thus, the entries are: 
    Alternatives, Criteria, Weight of each criterion and flags that indicate whether the criterion is 
    monotonic cost or monotonic benefit.
